{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb945232c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1395w–103"},"text":"§ 1395w–103.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Access to a choice of qualified prescription drug coverage","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb945232d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Assuring access to a choice of coverage","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb945232e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Choice of at least two plans in each area","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall ensure that each part D eligible individual has available, consistent with paragraph (2), a choice of enrollment in at least 2 qualifying plans (as defined in paragraph (3)) in the area in which the individual resides, at least one of which is a prescription drug plan. In any such case in which such plans are not available, the part D eligible individual shall be given the opportunity to enroll in a fallback prescription drug plan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb947942f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Requirement for different plan sponsors","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The requirement in paragraph (1) is not satisfied with respect to an area if only one entity offers all the qualifying plans in the area.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb9479430-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Qualifying plan defined","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this section, the term “qualifying plan” means—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idb9479431-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/a/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a prescription drug plan; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idb9479432-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/a/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" an MA–PD plan described in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–21/a/2/A/i"},"text":"section 1395w–21(a)(2)(A)(i) of this title","children":[],"tail":" that provides—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idb9479433-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/a/3/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" basic prescription drug coverage; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idb9479434-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/a/3/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" qualified prescription drug coverage that provides supplemental prescription drug coverage so long as there is no MA monthly supplemental beneficiary premium applied under the plan, due to the application of a credit against such premium of a rebate under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–24/b/1/C"},"text":"section 1395w–24(b)(1)(C) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb9479435-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Flexibility in risk assumed and application of fallback plan","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In order to ensure access pursuant to subsection (a) in an area—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb9479436-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the Secretary may approve limited risk plans under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–111/f"},"text":"section 1395w–111(f) of this title","children":[],"tail":" for the area; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb9479437-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–103/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" only if such access is still not provided in the area after applying paragraph (1), the Secretary shall provide for the offering of a fallback prescription drug plan for that area under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1395w–111/g"},"text":"section 1395w–111(g) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb9479438-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1935-08-14/ch531"},"text":"Aug. 14, 1935, ch. 531","children":[],"tail":", title XVIII, § 1860D–3, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/173/tI/s101/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–173, title I, § 101(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2003-12-08"},"text":"Dec. 8, 2003","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/117/2081"},"text":"117 Stat. 2081","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
